::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} How did you get to Xianzhou?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502113110-->
::'''Dongsheng:''' Xianzhou? You mean the Celestial Hall?
::'''Dongsheng:''' I was cutting wood in the mountains one day when I saw a giant ship. Not the type that floats on water, but... but one that floats in air like a feather. It floated towards the temple we built for the celestial lady.
::'''Dongsheng:''' I thought it must be other celestials here to take her back! So I ran and ran, and saw that the ship had landed, and there was a hole at the bottom.
::'''Dongsheng:''' It's weird &mdash; {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mister}}, how can a ship still sail with a hole in it? Anyway, I climbed in and fell asleep. The next thing I knew, I was here at the Celestial Hall!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502113118-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502113118-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} How could you even have fallen asleep?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502113122-->
:::'''Dongsheng:''' I was tired from all that running.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502113123-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502113123-->
:::'''Dongsheng:''' And then, some celestial soldiers in armor discovered me. They gave me a poke with some needle, and I could suddenly understand celestial speech.
:::'''Dongsheng:''' They asked me a few questions, and then dressed me in new clothes. Heehee, these clothes have no holes or patches on them. So pretty...
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Your life is truly intertwined with the celestials...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502113124-->
:::'''Dongsheng:''' Heehee, isn't that right? My Ma even said that fortune favors me because I have a giant forehead!
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502113123-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502113123-->
:::'''Dongsheng:''' And then, some celestial soldiers in armor discovered me. They gave me a poke with some needle, and I could suddenly understand celestial speech.
:::'''Dongsheng:''' They asked me a few questions, and then dressed me in new clothes. Heehee, these clothes have no holes or patches on them. So pretty...
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} How do you take care of yourself here?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502113115-->
::'''Dongsheng:''' I'm young, but I've lived through plenty of droughts and floods! I'm so awesome that I can go for three straight days without food!
::'''Dongsheng:''' But thanks to the kind celestials in this Celestial Hall, I have food and a place to live. That storyteller mister at Sleepless Earl gives me money for listening to my stories. He's so good!
::'''Dongsheng:''' Don't worry, {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mister}}. I heard that one day in heaven is a year on land. Time is running out. I'll go home once I find the celestial lady and get celestial medicine from her.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Exit}} I have nothing else to ask.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502113119-->
::Bye-bye! I need to keep searching for the celestial lady. {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mister}}, your dreams will certainly come true as well in Xianzhou!
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
