::'''Dongsheng:''' {{MC|f=Big sister|m=Big brother}}, are you a celestial too? Why do you look different from the rest of them?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I don't think I am...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502113003-->
:::'''Dongsheng:''' Huh? You're not a celestial? Then you must be seeking celestials, just like I am?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Other celestials?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502113005-->
:::'''Dongsheng:''' Yes, this is the Novenus Empyrea, where all celestials reside! Huh? {{MC|f=Big sister|m=Big brother}}, you're not a celestial? Then you must be seeking celestials, just like I am?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm a celestial too!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502113007-->
:::'''Dongsheng:''' Really? Forgive my dullness, but {{MC|f=big sister|m=big brother}}, you don't exude that celestial air...
:::'''Dongsheng:''' You look so different from the celestial men and women here. I just can't see {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mister}} as a celestial.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502113008-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502113008-->
::'''Dongsheng:''' Ooh, I forgot to introduce myself. I'm Dongsheng. I followed a celestial lady here. But... she doesn't know that.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_502011301_376-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_502011301_376-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Who is this celestial lady?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502113010-->
:::'''Dongsheng:''' She is... a lady who is both heavenly and celestial.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Let's not be superstitious!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502113012-->
:::'''Dongsheng:''' She's not some old wives' tale! Everyone knows who she is where I'm from! I even saw her using celestial magic to save my entire village!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502113013-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502113013-->
::'''Dongsheng:''' The older folks in the village say there are nine layers of heaven, with a palace at the very top where the eternally youthful celestials live. I thought it was just a fairy tale, but it's actually true!
::'''Dongsheng:''' I want to become a celestial too, but Dad said only those who have reached the pinnacle of cultivation may enter the Celestial Hall, drink osmanthus wine, and feast on chicken drumsticks with the gods!
::'''Dongsheng:''' I don't know what cultivation is, so I thought I'd never get the chance to eat chicken drumsticks, but here I am at the Celestial Hall!
::'''Dongsheng:''' It's just that I haven't found the celestial lady since I arrived, and that makes me sad. {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mister}}, is there anything else you want to ask?
;(Subsequent interactions)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 90000076: Config/Level/NPC/W2/NPC_DefaultStory_502011304.json-->
